  <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, Relicare excludes liability for loss arising from use of or reliance on the website or quiz output. Nothing in these terms excludes liability that cannot lawfully be excluded.</p>

  <!-- 10 -->
  <h2>10. Privacy and cookies</h2>
  <p>Your use of the website is also subject to our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Notice</a> and Cookies Policy.</p>

  <!-- 11 -->
  <h2>11. Changes to these terms</h2>
  <p>We may update these terms from time to time. The version published on the website at the relevant time will apply.</p>

  <!-- 12 -->
